                <h3>Set up your store</h3>
                <p>Add your products, warehouses, and team members. Import your existing catalog from a CSV.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-connector"></div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h3>Import daily sales</h3>
                <p>Export orders from your marketplace seller center. Upload the CSV. StockLedger matches SKUs and deducts stock.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-connector"></div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h3>See the truth</h3>
                <p>Real-time stock levels, profit margins by channel, and tax-ready invoices. All in one dashboard.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

