<!-- ═══ FAQ ═══ -->
<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="section-label">FAQ</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is there a free plan?</h3>
                <p>We offer a 14-day free trial with full Professional features. After that, plans start at Rp299K/month.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Do you charge per transaction?</h3>
                <p>Never. Unlike marketplaces, we charge a flat monthly fee regardless of how many orders you process.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I switch plans?</h3>
                <p>Yes, anytime. Upgrade or downgrade — changes take effect on your next billing cycle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What happens to my data if I cancel?</h3>
                <p>Your data stays in read-only mode for 30 days. You can export everything as CSV at any time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Does it connect to marketplaces automatically?</h3>
                <p>Currently via CSV import (you export from your seller center and upload). Direct API sync is on our roadmap.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is my data safe?</h3>
                <p>All data is encrypted in transit (HTTPS), isolated per tenant, with full audit trails and automatic backups.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

